commits.name: Commit-0
commits.content:
extends ./_extends/extends_html5_prototype.pug

block variables
  - var title = 'index'

block content 
  main#main.cl-main
      header.cl-header
        h1 프로젝트 코딩리스트
      .prototype-menu
        ul
          li.active
            a(href=`${path}/src/html/cl.html`) 페이지 리스트
          li
            a(href=`${path}/src/html/_prototype/prototype_list.html`) 프로토타입
          li
            a(href=`${path}/src/html/_prototype/prototype_layout.html`) 레이아웃
          li
            a(href=`${path}/src/html/_prototype/prototype_form.html`) 폼 양식
          li
            a(href=`${path}/src/html/_prototype/prototype_components_list.html`) 컴포넌트
      .table-container
        .table-scroll-inner
          // pages
          include ./_extends/cl_pages.pug
block script
  script.
    const tdNumber = document.querySelectorAll('td.no');

    tdNumber.forEach((tdList, index) => {
      tdList.innerText = index + 1;
    });
